mobile = rbind(mobile041206,mobile041004)
zz = rbind(zcard,zaccount)
l = list(card,mobile,life,ticket,zz)
preprocessing = function(df){
  names(df)[1]='id'
  data_date = separate(df,pay_time,c('dt','t'),sep=' ') %>%
    separate(t,c('h','m','s'),sep=':') %>%
    subset(select=1:3) %>%
    separate(dt,c('Y','M','d'),remove = FALSE) %>%
    subset(select=-3)
  data_date[,'dt':=as.Date(dt)]
  data_date = subset(data_date,dt>=as.Date("2016-03-01"))
  setorder(data_date,id,dt,M )
  return(data_date)
}
gg = function(i=1,title='信用卡还款'){ggplot(gather(p[[i]],key = type,value = b,-dt),
                        mapping = aes(x=dt,y=b,colour= type))+
    geom_line()+
    theme(text=element_text(family="Kai"))+
    labs(x='',y='',colour='',title=title)}

DataPreprocessing

q = list()
for(i in 1:5){
  q[[i]] = preprocessing(l[[i]])
}
p = list()
for(i in 1:5){
  p[[i]] = q[[i]][,.(订单数=.N,用户数=uniqueN(id)),by=dt] 
}

  • 每月分布
per_M = data.table(月份=1:12)
for(i in 1:5){
  per_M = cbind(per_M,q[[i]][,.N,by=M][order(M)])
}
per_M = subset(per_M,select = seq(1,11,2))
names(per_M) = c('月份','信用卡还款','手机充值','生活缴费','其他','转账')
g = data.table(gather(per_M,key = type,value = b,-月份))
ggplot(g,mapping = aes(x=factor(月份),y=log10(b),group=type,colour=type))+
  geom_line()+
  geom_point()+
  theme(text=element_text(family="Kai"))+
  labs(x='',y='',colour='')

per_M = data.table(time=1:31)

names(per_M) = c('time','信用卡还款','手机充值','生活缴费','其他','转账')
